{"tid":388234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇有人日日同人講坐過監好威威","createTime":"2017-09-05T10:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T14:39:30.000Z","uid":105945,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"445e92de9821376c079f12d877bce64c2a7a2a2f","tid":388234,"uid":105945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"好唔明有啲人坐完監好似好威咁<br />\n知唔知醜字點寫<br />\n如果我坐過監<br />\n出返黎第一件事就係去改名<br />\n唔想俾人知道自己的醜事<br />\n死監躉<br />\n咁唔要臉的人都有"},{"pid":"af45d3064678f500b5882935cfbf13ff88a9ad9e","tid":388234,"uid":105945,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"我一開始見到agentcc就有依個想法<br />\n我實在唔明點解咁多人吹奏一個監躉<br />\n當時亦都見到有少數人同我一樣想法<br />\n但點解正常人咁少"},{"pid":"aac54125d07854970bbeaebe1828a4c66daa8dfd","tid":388234,"uid":58527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"我都想試下坐監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入面實好多野玩<br />\n又唔洗返工比租愁衣食"},{"pid":"a301d591bb5009a015c06bb1d55fbde67701a138","tid":388234,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"睇下衰咩，衰十一仲會同人講咩"},{"pid":"ebdac39e00b14c5f258a52ed91ebcc09d9c544da","tid":388234,"uid":105945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想試下坐監 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入面實好多野玩<br />\n又唔洗返工比租愁衣食</blockquote><br />\n無電話 無上網 可以玩咩?"},{"pid":"e84449f25961faa58eb5b29bc9829b748c1be68f","tid":388234,"uid":105945,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下衰咩，衰十一仲會同人講咩</blockquote><br />\n衰十一 如果普通男歡女愛 大家歲數相近唔係咩大件事"},{"pid":"8a28033ce1bca1532c86df0e1740babd34fb80af","tid":388234,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"坐監唔係威, 但坐完出嚟生活好過你啲所謂好市民就確係威."},{"pid":"82b4f81d43e2e71c94492299a6e389a55e3ccb9a","tid":388234,"uid":342